eligibility.exclusivecriteria:
-  Previous hypnosis preparation for childbirth;

          -  poor understanding of English requiring translator;

          -  women who are already enrolled in another pregnancy trial where analgesia requirements
             are an outcome measure;

          -  active psychological or psychiatric problems such as: active depression requiring
             treatment by a psychiatrist;

          -  schizophrenia;

          -  prior psychosis;

          -  severe intellectual disability.

          -  Women with pain caused by specific pathological entities such as: congenital
             neuromuscular disorders; spina bifida; metastatic disease; osteoporosis; rheumatoid
             arthritis; fractures,are also excluded
